## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification (after implementation)

**Backend:**
```
cd d:\Developments\College Project\taskflow-backend
npm run dev
# In browser: http://localhost:5000/health → should return {"status":"OK"}
```

**Web App:**
```
cd d:\Developments\College Project\taskflow-app
npm run dev
# Open http://localhost:5173
# Login with seeded credentials, navigate all pages
```

**Mobile (Expo):**
```
cd d:\Developments\College Project\taskflow-mobile
npx expo start
# Scan QR with Expo Go app on phone, or press 'w' for web
# Test: Login → Dashboard → Tasks → Calendar → Team → Notifications → Profile
# Test: Logout → Forgot Password OTP flow
```
